task.summary: More handles take now colors and size from DrawingView.
Increases max nodes per layer to Integer.MAX_VALUE.
Fixes issues in FontableFigure and TextStrokeableFigure.
Removes module JSR 305 due to copyright issues.
Bumps retention of nullity annotations to "CLASS".
The default value of SHAPE must be a Rectangle.
Fixes compiler warnings. Always copies input arrays.
Implements support for exporting javafx Text nodes with line wrapping.
Minor bug fixes in CSS support.
Adds diagrammer sample and supporting classes.
Removes annotation from exception in catch-clause because this annotation crashes the compiler.
First steps towards a modular version of JHotDraw 8.
